## Quick Start (short version)

1) Flash Pico:
- Drag `6x6_test_pico.ino.uf2` onto the Pico (BOOTSEL mode)

2) Flash ESP8266:
- Upload `lumi_con_esp_integrated_0_0_4.ino`
- IMPORTANT: disconnect Pico GP0 → ESP RX during ESP flashing

3) Join WiFi:
- Connect to `Lumi-Con-Setup` and configure WiFi at `http://192.168.4.1`

4) Install plugin:
- Build/install plugin v5.2 (`npm install` → `npx lumia-plugin validate .` → `npx lumia-plugin build ...`)
- Enable Listener, set port (default 8787)

5) Select mode:
- On device boot: press Key 1 (Legacy) or Key 2 (Confirmed)

